5 of subsection A of Section 991a of Title 22 of the Oklahoma Statutes
6 under conditions determined by the Department of Corrections. The
7 jury shall be advised that the mandatory post-imprisonment
8 supervision shall be in addition to the actual imprisonment.
9 F. Any person responsible for the health, safety or welfare of
10 a child who shall willfully or maliciously engage in child sexual
